{"tid":2303533,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《理大圍城》贏荷蘭電影節剪接獎","createTime":"2020-11-28T04:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T05:10:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d83cce138f43fd8b76bd7388d82780b621010ff4","tid":2303533,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T04:52:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201128/LJ5OFGNQU5BKZI26NXHL3X7W4Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201128%2FLJ5OFGNQU5BKZI26NXHL3X7W4Y%2F&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7ChyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=6e9bfc11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201128%2FLJ5OFGNQU5BKZI26NXHL3X7W4Y%2F&h=6481aace\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201128/LJ5OFGNQU5BKZI26NXHL3X7W4Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n《理大圍城》贏荷蘭電影節剪接獎<br />\n<br />\n逆權紀錄片《理大圍城》早前入圍荷蘭阿姆斯特丹國際紀錄片電影節 （IDFA），昨日凌晨發行商影意志公佈，由「香港紀錄片工作者」拍攝的《理大圍城》贏得IDFA最佳剪接獎。頒獎禮以online形式舉行，在宣佈《理大圍城》獲獎時，播出一條香港紀錄片工作者代表的英語謝辭，<span class=\"orange\">「對我們，對香港都別具意義，在極權國家，人想自由及有尊嚴地活着，就必然有反抗，也必然有悲劇，『理大事件』是香港一道未癒合的傷口，也是香港歷史重要的一頁，盼望終有一天電影能除去格仔，讓每一雙勇敢、捍衞着自由的眼神都能被看到，請繼續關注香港和其他國家受壓迫的人們&hellip;&hellip;」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/u-KyGnsn1W-IFj84NTvFM4RNIgo=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RIFI2SYPKZB5JGXLPB5L3OK6MM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fu-KyGnsn1W-IFj84NTvFM4RNIgo%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRIFI2SYPKZB5JGXLPB5L3OK6MM.jpg&h=0ba8b406&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■崔允信樂見發行的《理大圍城》揚威海外，提醒大家毋忘記憶的責任。劇照<br />\n<br />\n致辭同時，紀錄片工作者代表由一個政府信封倒出一堆光碟碎片，還原砌成一隻碟。回應早前《理大圍城》送到香港電檢處的光碟，變成「理大碎片」交還發行商，電檢處解釋「光碟是在影碟機內碎裂」。發行商負責人崔允信接受《蘋果》訪問，他以短訊回覆：「𠵱家落嚟我哋係要更加努力，令更多人睇到香港人又好，香港以外地方又好。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qfO7HYwRwBDOEvUlf9525ABQLGE=/640x800/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EIQETSDXHFAXDISI5BP5SQD67U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqfO7HYwRwBDOEvUlf9525ABQLGE%3D%2F640x800%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEIQETSDXHFAXDISI5BP5SQD67U.jpg&h=0f861407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n崔允信 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/F9j4jtkRfrrpO5C_kxvg1RYYTbY=/640x420/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3OLMETK4SNFPXOB5AS5JFWFAU4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FF9j4jtkRfrrpO5C_kxvg1RYYTbY%3D%2F640x420%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3OLMETK4SNFPXOB5AS5JFWFAU4.jpg&h=e6bde20d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■致辭時，紀錄片工作者代表將「理大碎片」還原砌成一隻碟。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n===========<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hk